      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom state, exhibiting impeccable mechanical integrity and an interior entirely devoid of wear. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection. This is not merely a pre-owned vehicle; it is a benchmark of its class.",
