    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Power is delivered via the legendary S54 inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing for razor-sharp throttle response. The chassis remains flawlessly rigid, with proactive subframe reinforcement and a fully documented rod bearing service ensuring mechanical longevity. The Getrag six-speed manual transmission shifts with tactile precision, sending power through a variable M differential lock. Finished in its original factory coating with zero paint correction required, this specimen showcases impeccable kinematic integrity and a pristine undercarriage. It is a concours-level example of BMW\u2019s high-revving heritage.",
